title: Pronouns
---
body:

My pronouns are **he/him** or **they/them**. Either one is okay!

Here's a <a href="https://www.mypronouns.org/they-them" target="_blank">quick explainer</a> on what they/them pronouns are, and some <a href="https://pronoun.monster/they/them/them/their/themself" target="_blank">example sentences</a>.
